comments: Ingles (UTA) makes contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) during the pick and disengages.
Crowder (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Connaughton's (MIL) path before the contact.
Favors (UTA) makes contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) body after he has gathered the ball on his drive to the rim.
Connaughton (MIL) makes marginal contact to Ingles (UTA) during his driving shot attempt.
Favors (UTA) makes marginal contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) during his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Connaughton (MIL) makes marginal contact to Mitchell's (UTA) arm, but does not affect his ability to control the ball.
Favors (UTA) is in Connaughton's (MIL) path before the pick and switch.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes incidental contact to Mitchell's (UTA) arm after the release and does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Korver (UTA) and Lopez (MIL) engage during the inbounds.
Crowder (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Connaughton's (MIL) path before the contact.
Middleton (MIL) makes contact to the arm of Favors (UTA) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
[Observable in enhanced video] From RATR, Favors (UTA) appears to fully clear the lane twice before receiving the pass.
Favors (UTA) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Connaughton (MIL) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Favors (UTA) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Mirotic (MIL) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Mitchell (UTA) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Middleton (MIL) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) extends his arm and dislodges O'Neale (UTA) during the rebound.
RATR and other angles show that O'Neale (UTA) may initially make some ball contact, but then comes down on Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm during his shooting motion, affecting his shot attempt.
